    <stitle>ALTERNATOR: DELCO-REMY 21-SI SERIES - REASSEMBLY - BRUSH HOLDER AND DIODE TRIO</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="assemble" graphiccount="1">
        <title>BRUSH HOLDER AND DIODE TRIO</title>
        <para>Refer to
            <hotlnk xrefid="f0801725">Figure 25</hotlnk>
            for Item numbers in parentheses.
        </para>
        <figure id="f0801725" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g0801725" filename="../figg08/G0801725.webp" type="webp" resolution="72"/>
            <caption>Installing Brush Holder and Diode Trio</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1>1. BRUSH PIN</callout1>
                <callout1>2. BRUSH HOLDER ASSEMBLY</callout1>
                <callout1>3. REGULATOR</callout1>
                <callout1>4. SRE HOUSING</callout1>
                <callout1>5. ATTACHING SCREW (PIVOT)</callout1>
                <callout1>6. REGULATOR ATTACHING SCREW (INSULATED)</callout1>
                <callout1>7. DIODE TRIO</callout1>
                <callout1>8. RECTIFIER BRIDGE</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">With brushes pinned in retracted position, install brush holder assembly (Item 2) to
                mounting holes in regulator (Item 3) and SRE housing (Item 4). Install brush holder attaching (pivot)
                screw (Item 5) and one insulated regulator attaching screw (Item 6); finger tighten both screws.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install diode trio (Item 7) onto 3 threaded studs on rectifier bridge assembly (Item 8).
                Position lone connector strap on diode trio over closest mounting hole in brush holder (Item 2) and
                regulator (Item 3).
            </para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
